%p.bomb_deactivated
  The bomb is deactivated.
  %p
    Please enter the activation code.
  %form{:action => "/activate", :method => "post"}
    %p 
      Activation code: 
      %input.act_code_guess{:name => "act_code", :type => "text", :pattern => "[0-9]{4}"}
    %p
      %input.submit_act_code_guess{:type => "submit", :value => "Submit activation code"}

  - if bomb.bad_activation_code
    %p.incorrect_act_code_submitted
      Incorrect activation code.
%p
  %a{:href => "/"} Reboot bomb?